    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Collections of writings in the form of a volume of learned articles or essays by colleagues, students, and admirers to honor a scholar, other person, institution, or society on a special occasion or anniversary. Festschriften are usually complimentary or memorial publications in the form of collected essays, addresses, or biographical, bibliographical, scientific, or other contributions, often embodying the results of research.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000050615/IFLA Glossary for Art Librarians (1984)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Colecciones de escritos producidos para honrar o celebrar a alguien o algo, generalmente en forma de un volumen de artículos eruditos o ensayos de colegas, estudiantes y admiradores para honrar a un erudito en un aniversario especial.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Boeken met wetenschappelijke artikelen of essays van collega's en bewonderaars, die dienen als eerbetoon of herinnering, vooral aan wetenschappers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099099/Van Dale groot woordenboek (1994)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>為表彰某位學者、人物、機構或學會，由其同事、學生及仰慕者在某特殊場合或周年紀念時刻創作，以單冊學術性質文章、評論為形式呈現之書寫集結。記念文集通常是種以集結論文、演說稿或傳記性、文獻性、科學性及其他類包含研究結果文件為形式所呈現之恭賀性或紀念性質出版品。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
